caption:
The NEWSLETTER exercise led by @jordan.seif was amazing!
-
Each leader wrote a news article of what life would look like 2-5 years out about @untdslr, their teams and their individual accomplishments. Each leader went on their own for 30 minutes and visualized what that would look like and put pen to paper. The take aways were incredible. 
-
It’s impossible to go somewhere clearly if you can’t see the destination. This exercise helps bridge the gap. 
-
Such an impactful exercise. Try it out. You will thank us later.
